362	  Plan-agent \texttt{lean\_run\_code} probe (iter-013) confirms it typechecks end-to-end against current Mathlib + project state, kernel-only axioms (\lstinline{propext}, \lstinline{Classical.choice}, \lstinline{Quot.sound}); $\Module.\mathtt{finrank}\,k\,(\HModulePrime\,k\,F\,n\,X) : \mathbb N$ also probes successfully through the abbrev's reducibility.
